This project provides a great service to the educational authorities
for their services in the field of exam development and electronic correction of article questions.

1- it help teachers to create exam manual and they can upload already exists exams

2- it allow for teacher to update there exams (edit , delete , add)

3- show old teacher exams that he is already create

for student it offers many services,including

1- it allow for student to access any exam throw enter exam id and exam date

2- he can solve this exam and he can see the degree in the same time

3- it save student exam in old exam (questions , teacher answers ,student answers , degree)

this app makes the exam and correction process easy